<html><head><title>Hunt</title></head> <body bgcolor="#000000" text="#FFFFFF" vlink = "#99cccc" link = "#99ccff"  topmargin=0leftmargin=0 ><TABLE border = "0" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="5"><TR><TD valign = middle align = left  height = 300 ><font size="+1">My story? Thirteen months incountry: One on chow hall duty; one in thehospital and the rest flying in the skies of South Vietnam almost everyday... 27 air medals to show in one piece of brass the times that went onfor a 20 year old who was once an altar boy in a Lutheran church and wasquiet... But the  Marine Corps and the Nam <A HREF = "hunt2.html">changed allthat</A>... forever and ever.</font> <p>JJoel Hunt Sr</TD></TR></table></body></html>